<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#8bf278d4ec71778283884c23741fcb1d>.
<#8bf278d4ec71778283884c23741fcb1d> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/COU_EUR_CDCC>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-04-14T17:12:17.597Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#8bf278d4ec71778283884c23741fcb1d> {
<http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/COU_EUR_CDCC> a <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept>;
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/deprecated> "true";
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#deprecated> true;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#exactMatch> <http://eurovoc.europa.eu/118>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Council for Cultural Cooperation"@en, "Consiliul pentru Cooperare Culturală"@ro, "Rat für kulturelle Zusammenarbeit"@de, "Съвет за културно сътрудничество"@bg, "Conseil de la coopération culturelle"@fr, "Kulttuuriyhteistyön neuvosto"@fi, "Rådet för kulturellt samarbete"@sv, "A Kulturális Együttműködés Tanácsa"@hu, "Svet za kulturno sodelovanje"@sl, "Kultūras sadarbības padome"@lv, "Kultūrinio bendradarbiavimo taryba"@lt, "Raad voor culturele samenwerking"@nl, "Consiglio della cooperazione culturale"@it, "Kunsill għal Kooperazzjoni Kulturali"@mt, "Συμβούλιο Πολιτιστικής Συνεργασίας"@el, "Rada pre kultúrnu spoluprácu"@sk, "Rada pro kulturní spolupráci"@cs, "Rada Współpracy Kulturalnej"@pl, "Vijeće za kulturnu suradnju"@hr, "Conselho de Cooperação Cultural"@pt, "Consejo de Cooperación Cultural"@es, "Kultuurikoostöö Nõukogu"@et, "Rådet for Kulturelt Samarbejde"@da, "Савет за културну сарадњу"@sr;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Council for Cultural Co-operation was set up as a committee of governmental representatives responsible for setting the agenda for action in the fields of education, culture, media, sport and youth. In 2001, the Committee of Ministers of the Council of Europe decided to transform the Council for Cultural Co-operation (CDCC) and its specialised Committees into four Steering Committees; including the Steering Committee for Culture (CDCULT) which had a \"hands-on\" mandate for developing cultural co-operation programmes."@en, "Le Conseil de coopération culturelle a été créé comme un comité de représentants gouvernementaux responsables de l’établissement du programme d’action dans les domaines de l’éducation, la culture, les médias, les sports et la jeunesse. En 2001, le Comité des Ministres du Conseil de l’Europe a décidé de transformer le Conseil de Coopération Culturelle (CDCC) et ses comités spécialisés en quatre comités de pilotage, y compris l’actuel Comité Directeur pour la Culture (CDCULT) qui a le mandat de développer des programmes de coopération culturelle."@fr;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "COU_EUR_CDCC"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "COU_EUR_CDCC"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "COB0001311"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "CDCC"@fr, "CDCC"@en, "Council for Cultural Cooperation of the Council of Europe"@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/COU_EUR_CDCC_1962_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "COU_EUR_CDCC";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/op-code> "COU_EUR_CDCC";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/op-code> "COU_EUR_CDCC";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/start.use> "1962-01-01";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/authority-code> "COU_EUR_CDCC";
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#broader> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/COU_EUR>;
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/end.use> "2001-12-31"
}
<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#8e272d9ae5ec5c5707a8bb6cacdd3105>.
<#8e272d9ae5ec5c5707a8bb6cacdd3105> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/COU_EUR_CDESR>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-04-14T17:12:17.602Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#8e272d9ae5ec5c5707a8bb6cacdd3105> {
<http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/COU_EUR_CDESR> a <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept>;
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/deprecated> "true";
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#deprecated> true;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Comité Diretor do Ensino Superior e da Investigação"@pt, "Comitetul Director pentru Învățământ Superior și Cercetare"@ro, "Kumitat tat-Tmexxija għall-Edukazzjoni Għolja u r-Riċerka"@mt, "Usmerjevalni odbor za visokošolsko izobraževanje in raziskave"@sl, "Augstākās izglītības un pētniecības koordinācijas komiteja"@lv, "Comité directeur de l’enseignement supérieur et de la recherche"@fr, "Korkeakoulutuksen ja tutkimuksen johtokomitea"@fi, "Aukštojo mokslo ir mokslinių tyrimų iniciatyvinis komitetas"@lt, "Управителен комитет за висше образование и научна дейност"@bg, "Steering Committee for Higher Education and Research"@en, "Riadiaci výbor pre vysokoškolské vzdelávanie a výskum"@sk;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Le programme de l’enseignement supérieur et de la recherche du Conseil de l’Europe a été supervisé par le Comité directeur de l’enseignement supérieur et de la recherche (CDESR). Alors que la plupart des comités du Conseil de l’Europe ne sont que des organes intergouvernementaux, le CDESR était un lieu de rencontre pour les représentants des ministères chargés de l’enseignement supérieur et pour la communauté universitaire."@fr, "The Council of Europe’s higher education and research programme was overseen by the Steering Committee for Higher Education and Research (CDESR). Whereas most Council of Europe committees are intergovernmental only, the CDESR was a meeting place for representatives both from Ministries responsible for higher education and the academic community."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "COU_EUR_CDESR"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "COU_EUR_CDESR"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "COB0001314"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "CDESR"@en, "CDESR"@fr;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/COU_EUR_CDESR_2002_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "COU_EUR_CDESR";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/op-code> "COU_EUR_CDESR";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/op-code> "COU_EUR_CDESR";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/start.use> "2002-01-01";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/authority-code> "COU_EUR_CDESR";
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#broader> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/COU_EUR>;
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/end.use> "2011-12-31"
}
<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#2c83f1d67e2b9ed43de5af4edc28ddcf>.
<#2c83f1d67e2b9ed43de5af4edc28ddcf> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/COU_EUR_CDED>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-04-14T17:12:17.607Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#2c83f1d67e2b9ed43de5af4edc28ddcf> {
<http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/COU_EUR_CDED> a <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept>;
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/deprecated> "true";
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#deprecated> true;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Comité directeur de l’éducation"@fr, "Riadiaci výbor pre vzdelávanie"@sk, "Kumitat tat-Tmexxija għall-Edukazzjoni"@mt, "Comitetul Director pentru Educație"@ro, "Koulutuksen johtokomitea"@fi, "Usmerjevalni odbor za izobraževanje"@sl, "Švietimo iniaciatyvinis komitetas"@lt, "Управителен комитет за образование"@bg, "Izglītības koordinācijas komiteja"@lv, "Steering Committee for Education"@en, "Comité Diretor da Educação"@pt;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Sous l’autorité du Comité des Ministres et dans le cadre de la Convention culturelle européenne, le Comité Directeur de l’Education était responsable de la mise en œuvre des activités éducatives scolaires et extrascolaires prévues au Programme adopté par le Comité des Ministres. Le Comité a établit des orientations pour le programme d’activités qu’il soumet au Comité des Ministres par l’entremise du Secrétaire Général. Ses propositions portaient en particulier sur : les stratégies et les réformes des politiques éducatives en ce qui concerne les questions d’actualité et les perspectives à plus long terme ; la construction d’une société démocratique, solidaire et pluraliste et la promotion de la compréhension mutuelle entre les peuples."@fr, "Under the authority of the Committee of Ministers and in the framework of the European Cultural Convention, the Steering Committee for Education was responsible for the implementation of school and out-of school educational activities included in the programme adopted by the Committee of Ministers. The Committee of Ministers should draw up guidelines for the programme of activities which it should submit to the Committee of Ministers through the Secretary General. Its proposals focused in particular on: education policy strategies and reforms relating to topical issues and longer-term prospects; building a democratic, caring and pluralist society and fostering mutual understanding between people."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "COU_EUR_CDED"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "COU_EUR_CDED"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "COB0001313"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "CDED"@fr, "CDED"@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/COU_EUR_CDED_2002_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "COU_EUR_CDED";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/op-code> "COU_EUR_CDED";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/op-code> "COU_EUR_CDED";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/start.use> "2002-01-01";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/authority-code> "COU_EUR_CDED";
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#broader> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/COU_EUR>;
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/end.use> "2011-12-31"
}
