    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Steering Committee for Culture, Heritage and Landscape superceded the previous specialised Committees in the field of culture, heritage and landscape – the Steering Committee for Education, the Steering Committee for Higher Education and Research, the Steering Committee for Culture and the Steering Committee for Cultural Heritage – and now oversees all the activities implemented by the Council of Europe in these sectors."@en;
