    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Rada auditorů ESVO"@cs, "Komisja Obrachunkowa EFTA"@pl, "Accountantscommissie van de EVA"@nl, "Odbor revizorjev Efte"@sl, "Бордът на одиторите на ЕАСТ"@bg, "Organo contabile dell’EFTA"@it, "EFTA Könyvvizsgálói Testület"@hu, "EFTA-Ausschuss der Rechnungsprüfer"@de, "EFTA audiitorite kogu"@et, "Odbor revizora EFTA-e"@hr, "Bord tal-Awdituri tal-EFTA"@mt, "EFTA-Revisionsudvalget"@da, "EFTAn tilintarkastuslautakunta"@fi, "ELPA auditorių valdyba"@lt, "Bord Iniúchóirí CSTE"@ga, "EFTA Board of Auditors"@en, "Junta de Auditores de la AELC"@es, "Rada audítorov EZVO"@sk, "Eftas revisionskommitté"@sv, "EBTA Revidentu padome"@lv, "Επιτροπή Ελεγκτών της ΕΖΕΣ"@el, "Conselho de Auditoria da EFTA"@pt, "Consiliul auditorilor AELS"@ro, "Comité des commissaires aux comptes de l’AELE"@fr;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The EFTA Board of Auditors is a permanent committee of EFTA auditors. Board meetings take place “at four” (one representative from each EFTA Member State) and “at three” (Iceland, Liechtenstein and Norway, with Switzerland as an observer). In cooperation with external auditors, the EFTA Board of Auditors performs an annual audit of the three EFTA institutions: the EFTA Secretariat, the EFTA Surveillance Authority and the EFTA Court. The EFTA Board of Auditors also works in cooperation with the European Court of Auditors. The Board members meet three times a year and are assisted in their work by an officer of the EFTA Secretariat."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "EFTA_BOA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "COB0001583"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "EFTA_BOA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/EFTA_BOA_1992_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "EFTA_BOA";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/op-code> "EFTA_BOA";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/op-code> "EFTA_BOA";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/start.use> "1992-05-01";
